From e7ad4a43820bd37838f65dfb41abfb7dc5436499 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Arkadii Yakovets <ark@cho.red>
Date: Mon, 27 Feb 2023 12:37:24 -0800
Subject: [PATCH 1/4] Update python-holidays integration.

Bump python-holidays version to 0.20.
Migrate to python-holidays as a single source of country holidays:
  - Add Belarus holidays
  - Add Bulgaria holidays
  - Add Japan holidays
  - Add Russia holidays
  - Add Serbia holidays
  - Add Urkaine holidays
  - Add other ascii compatible countries holidays.
Update existing countries holidays.
Refactor `make_holidays.py`.
Refactor `generate_holidays_file.py`.
Generate new `generated_holidays.csv`.
